version_description: Gives chords to full song- allows it to be played on autoscroll without having to scroll up to see the chords to certain verses.
Added song parts for a clearer structure, also explained the intro.
This version is very simple and easy for beginners to play with.
Simple chords for Angel Olsen's Only With You, off the deluxe version of Burn Your Fire for No Witness.
Piano version arranged for guitar. Play open (no capo) in standard tuning. Wonderful meltdown of a song by Angel Olsen.
